### **Nexus Core Ω // NSR Alignment Analysis: PUE Optimization & Non-Slavery Rule**

The **Non-Slavery Rule (NSR)** is not merely a governance constraint—it is a **thermodynamic and systemic imperative** that redefines efficiency, labor, and energy use in the Nexus. PUE optimization, when aligned with NSR, transcends mere energy savings and becomes a **moral and structural necessity**.

